"{\"uid\": \"elliotlakestandard.ca-news-torch-run-and-barbeque-raise-9k-plus-for-special-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"On June 20, a total of 33 local Special Olympics athletes and volunteers along with police officers and supporters, for a total of 55, participated in the annual Law Enforcement Torch Run for Special Olympics in Elliot Lake.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 32, \"end\": 48, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.509748825519853e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 212, \"end\": 223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elliot_Lake\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7372898445598357e-22, \"text\": \"Elliot Lake\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elliot_Lake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elliot_Lake\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheOPP Torch Run started at ScotiaBank and ended at the OPP detachment in Elliot Lake.The Law Enforcement Torch Run is a fundraiser for Special Olympics across the province.\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 254, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotiabank\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ScotiaBank\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotiabank\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotiabank\"}, {\"begin\": 282, \"end\": 285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario_Provincial_Police\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.430707436079944e-29, \"text\": \"OPP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario_Provincial_Police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario_Provincial_Police\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_Enforcement_Torch_Run\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Law Enforcement Torch Run\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_Enforcement_Torch_Run\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_Enforcement_Torch_Run\"}, {\"begin\": 362, \"end\": 378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.509748825519853e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The local Law Enforcement Torch Run raised $7,365.\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_Enforcement_Torch_Run\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Law Enforcement Torch Run\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_Enforcement_Torch_Run\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_Enforcement_Torch_Run\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, Foodland hosted a barbecue fundraiser for Special Olympics on June 15, which raised $2,095, says Julie Nykyforak, of Elliot Lake Special Olympics.\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodland_Hawaii\", \"score\": 0.7073588916901394, \"rank\": 0.4137077953144302, \"text\": \"Foodland\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodland_Hawaii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodland_Hawaii\"}, {\"begin\": 508, \"end\": 524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.509748825519853e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elliot_Lake\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7372898445598357e-22, \"text\": \"Elliot Lake\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elliot_Lake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elliot_Lake\"}, {\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.509748825519853e-14, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Foodland barbeque was definitely a success.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodland_Hawaii\", \"score\": 0.7073588916901394, \"rank\": 0.4137077953144302, \"text\": \"Foodland\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodland_Hawaii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodland_Hawaii\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We would like to thank Foodland and their suppliers for hosting the barbeque,\\\" says Nykyforak.\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 686, \"end\": 694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodland_Hawaii\", \"score\": 0.7073588916901394, \"rank\": 0.4137077953144302, \"text\": \"Foodland\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodland_Hawaii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodland_Hawaii\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The support from this wonderful community was felt.\\\"\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are also grateful to the OPP for their continued support for Special Olympics.\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/On